author: crossley
msg: Add crude method with <a name="XXX"/> to get section id.
Enable better fragment identifiers than the default, which is to URLencode
the title. Such fragment identifiers get really nasty with verbose titles.

author: leif
msg: Fix a problem where value sample history would be incorrectly reset to 0 when the sample had not been viewed or received any new values for longer than the total sample period.

author: leif
msg: Add additional instruments to track the objects internal to the instrument manager.
Fix some problems where instrument elements defined multiple times in the configuration file would cause problems.
